%% Agent topology — orchestrator + sub-agents + tools + HITL
flowchart TB
    EVT["Event<br/>(port congestion,<br/>ETA slip)"] --> ORCH
    USR["User query<br/>via Joule"] --> ORCH

    ORCH["Orchestrator<br/>(Planner LLM)"]

    ORCH -->|plan + delegate| DA["Data Retrieval Agent"]
    ORCH --> RA["Risk Analyst Agent"]
    ORCH --> AG["Alt Generator Agent"]
    ORCH --> IS_A["Impact Scorer Agent"]
    ORCH --> CA["Communication Agent"]

    DA -->|SQL / OData| BDC[("BDC Data Products")]
    RA -->|rules + LLM| BDC
    AG -->|tool: find_alt_suppliers,<br/>find_alt_routes,<br/>find_stock_transfers| BDC
    IS_A -->|cost / SLA / tier model| BDC
    CA -->|drafts notes| EMAIL["Email / Teams / Slack"]

    ORCH --> HITL["Human-in-the-Loop<br/>(Supply Chain Head)"]
    HITL -->|approve| EXEC["SAP Integration Suite<br/>→ ERPs (execute)"]
